really does
come to us from light.

45:04.535 --> 45:08.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have telescopes that span
the range
of light to take pictures of the
sky. This

45:08.806 --> 45:12.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
