they do, and there is this great
discovery.

47:42.827 --> 47:46.964 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, yes, there is fighting
along the way.
There is competition. There are
failures and

47:46.997 --> 47:50.835 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
successes. And at the end of the
