48:36.714 --> 48:38.115 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JANNA LEVIN: Yes.

48:38.149 --> 48:40.718 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So you like
combining the storytelling
of the science.

48:40.751 --> 48:42.553 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JANNA LEVIN: Right.

48:42.586 --> 48:45.022 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I would be talking to Rai
