49:17.388 --> 49:18.722 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JANNA LEVIN: Yes. Yes.

49:18.756 --> 49:21.058 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: It was a shock
