49:41.478 --> 49:43.214 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: And then?

49:43.247 --> 49:47.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANNA LEVIN: And then it struck.
