50:07.071 --> 50:08.906 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JANNA LEVIN: Yes. Yes.

50:08.939 --> 50:11.041 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So when you look
at what comes
from this, give us some sense of
what it might

50:11.075 --> 50:12.877 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
mean.

50:12.910 --> 50:15.779 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANNA LEVIN: So, I remember when
I was a young
student listening to Kip talk
about this,

50:15.813 --> 50:20.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
